any subpages to “Tabs” as you like, depending on the number of tabs you want on the frontpage, and StoreFront will take care of the rest! For information on displaying products from WooCommerce or other posts in the tabs, read-up on using our News Show Pro widget as a shortcode here.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/tabbed-content.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1984\" src=\"{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/tabbed-content.png\" alt=\"tabbed-content\" width=\"1206\" height=\"1063\" /></a>','Tabbed content','','inherit','open','open','','1925-revision-v1','','','2014-05-20 08:05:28','2014-05-20 08:05:28','',1925,'{$page_url}/?p=1985',0,'revision','',0),(1235,1,'2013-12-16 08:48:35','2013-12-16 08:48:35','StoreFront Theme has an eCommerce plugin integrated, that helps you to sell anything.\r\n\r\nFull documentation of this plugin can be found <a title=\"WooCommerce documentation\" href=\"http://docs.woothemes.com/\">here.</a>\r\n\r\nWe added some features to this plugin, namely:\r\n<ul data-style=\"style1\">\r\n	<li>Short description can be visible on catalog pages,</li>\r\n	<li>it is possible to specify the number of characters of short description (If enabled),</li>\r\n	<li>it is possible to specify a sidebar position on Woocommerce pages,</li>\r\n	<li>it is possible to specify a sidebar width on Woocommerce pages,</li>\r\n	<li>it is possible to disable/enable loop buttons (add to cart, select options) on woocommerce catalog pages</li>\r\n	<li>Popup cart can be visible at the top part of the page (you have to add Woocommerce cart into Cart widget area and enable \"Woocommerce cart\" option from Page tab)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/cart.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1895\" src=\"{$page_url}/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/cart.png\" alt=\"cart\" width=\"567\" height=\"450\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIt is possible to change above options in StoreFront –&gt;Template options –&gt; Page tab.\r\n\r\nWoocommerce template files are overriden in StoreFront/woocoomerce directory.\r\n\r\nAll woocommerce styles are located in StoreFront/css/woocommerce.css file.\r\n\r\nThere are functions used in this woocommerce plugin in StoreFront/gavern/wc-functions.php file. Here, you can find options, e. g. to display amount of products per page, change the number of products per row (Using Woocommerce hooks).\r\n\r\nThe appearance of a Woocommerce plugin was praperad especially for StoreFront Theme and is strictly connected with theme files. We made sure that the plugin is fully responsive (as the theme). We do not recommend to enable WooCommerce CSS. You can choose one of the nine plugin’s color versions. (matched to the appearance of the theme).','Woocommerce Features','','publish','open','open','','woocommerce-features','','','2014-05-19 08:52:54','2014-05-19 08:52:54','',0,'{$page_url}/?page_id=1235',0,'page','',0),(1309,1,'2013-12-17 08:46:42','2013-12-17 08:46:42','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus lectus neque, mattis vitae sagittis eu, porttitor mattis leo. Aenean porta, est ac accumsan mollis, justo metus commodo justo, at posuere nulla eros in est. Quisque metus diam, porta ac elit vel, congue facilisis sem. Aliquam nec egestas ipsum, sit amet pretium justo. Morbi vehicula risus ac libero viverra tincidunt. Nulla in gravida risus. Sed eget ornare lacus.\r\n<div class=\"gk-columns\" data-column-count=\"3\">\r\n<div><strong>Material information</strong>[ulist style=\"1\"]\r\n66 % Cotton,\r\n34% Elastomultiester.\r\n[/ulist]</div>\r\n<div><strong>Fit &amp; sizing</strong>[ulist style=\"1\"]\r\nSit just below waist,\r\nSlim fit through leg.\r\n[/ulist]</div>\r\n<div><strong>Care informations</strong>[ulist style=\"1\"]\r\nMachine Wash Warm,\r\nDryclean Only P,\r\nDo Not Tumble Dry.\r\n[/ulist]</div>\r\n</div>','Wool-Silk Scalloped Pant','','publish','open','closed','','alice-skinny-jeans','','','2014-05-13 07:11:29','2014-05